        LODSD
        PUSH     EAX
        PUSH     EDX

        LODSD
        PUSH     EAX
        PUSH     EDX

        LODSD
        PUSH     EAX
        PUSH     EDX

        MOV      ESI, offset[ SelectObject ]
        CALL     ESI
        CALL     ESI
